| `03-consumables.md` | 763 → ~51K | ✅ CLEANED | Ammunition, Oils, Potions, Scrolls, Talismans |
| `04-held-items.md` | 323 → ~25K | ✅ CLEANED | Held items (bag of holding, broom of flying, crystal ball, etc.) |
